I just got back from a bike ride. Hot and tired. It's already 96 here. I'm afraid we might actually reach the 105 that some people are predicting. Ouch!&nbsp; 

My boyfriend lives in Denver where they've had much rain for weeks. He called me the other day and said that it was flooded where he lived. Lots of toronadoes, tornado warnings. Crazy. 

What's it like where you are?&nbsp;
